lead_paragraph: Valencia coach Gary Neville, pained by a 7-0 mauling at Barcelona in the King’s Cup, must pick up his team for Sunday’s trip to Real Betis where he will be looking for a first win in nine La Liga matches.

headline.print_headline: Neville Looks to Pick Up the Valencia Pieces at Betis
